{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d16aa23505","title":"林彪关于支左问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"465c271c4d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"d16aa23505"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f3cbf4fcf2","type":"title","text":"关于支左问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505"},{"id":"3dd30d48bc","type":"authors","text":"林彪","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505"},{"id":"c368ccf387","type":"paragraph","text":"要学老三篇，破“私”立公。共产主义就是讲的一个公字，反对一个“私”字。要破“私”立公，不然就在那里扯皮。要解决问题，就要从灵魂深处爆发革命。有错误不改，就是不好，干部、战士，不要以为学了毛主席著作就行了，学了不用那是空话。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505"},{"id":"b11adf4e40","type":"paragraph","text":"千头万绪就是要破“私”。破“私”，要打进攻战，光打防御战不是马列主义。拥护我们伟大领袖毛主席的人是革命的，公和“私”的标准就是拥护还是反对我们的伟大领袖毛主席。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505"},{"id":"4ecae3306b","type":"paragraph","text":"（郑维山、陈先瑞汇报工作后林副主席的指示）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505"}],"page":{"id":"8d7153f923","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d16aa23505","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}